videos.description: Ben Hicks zips a pass to James Proche who runs down the sideline for a 86-yard touchdown giving SMU an early lead.
videos.headline: SMU's Proche rips off 86-yard catch and run TD

videos.description: UCF's McKenzie Milton's pass is intercepted by Mikial Onu on the first drive giving SMU the ball back in the first quarter.
videos.headline: SMU defense gets to Milton early

videos.description: McKenzie Milton finds Marlon Williams down field for a 46-yard gain which moves the Knights down field and sets up a touchdown.
videos.headline: Milton bounces back with big pass for UCF

videos.description: McKenzie Milton keeps the ball and runs it in from the 9 yard line to tie the game in the first quarter.
videos.headline: UCF scores on 9-yard TD run from Milton

videos.description: Ke'Mon Freeman makes a run for the end zone but Tre Neal knocks the ball from his hands and recovers the fumble for a touchback.
videos.headline: UCF recovers fumble in the end zone for a touchback

videos.description: McKenzie Milton hits Gabriel Davis down field and he beats the defenders to the end zone for a 80-yard touchdown giving the Knights the lead.
videos.headline: UCF scores on huge 80-yard catch and run

videos.description: McKenzie Milton's pass is picked off by Jordan Wyatt and returned 36-yards for a touchdown to tie the game.
videos.headline: SMU defense ties game with pick-six

videos.description: Adrian Killins Jr.  dodges defenders on his 34-yard touchdown run to put UCF in the lead late in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Knights score on speedy 34-yard TD run

videos.description: UCF head coach Scott Frost says that the first half was sloppy and they are going to make the adjustments at half time to clean it up.
videos.headline: Frost wants cleaner play in second half

videos.description: Ben Hicks throws on the run and Courtland Sutton makes a tough catch on the sideline staying in bounds for a Mustang's first down.
videos.headline: Sutton makes sweet sideline catch for SMU

videos.description: Adrian Killins Jr. runs up the middle and breaks free from a tackle to score a 64-yard touchdown adding to the Knight's lead.
videos.headline: UCF's Killins breaks tackle and scores 64-yard TD

videos.description: Jordan Akins hauls in a pass but then Jordan Wyatt forces him to fumble to give the Mustangs the ball back at their own 7 yard line.
videos.headline: SMU defense forces fumble in red zone

videos.description: Xavier Jones powers into the end zone from the 2 yard line to make it a one possession game late in the third quarter.
videos.headline: SMU cuts UCF's lead with short TD run

videos.description: McKenzie Milton connects with Tre'Quan Smith down field and he breaks a tackle to move the Knights in to scoring position.
videos.headline: UCF moves down field with 63-yard catch from Smith

videos.description: Delontae Scott gets to McKenzie Milton and throws him down on the sack for a loss of 12 yards to end the Knight's drive.
videos.headline: Scott gets big sack to end UCF's drive
